      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<section class=\"reviews-section\">\n  <h2 class=\"reviews-heading\">What people are saying</h2>\n\n  <div class=\"reviews-track-wrap\">\n    <div class=\"reviews-track\">\n\n      <div class=\"review-card\">\n        <div class=\"stars\">★★★★★</div>\n        <p class=\"review-text\">Applied it before a beach trip and it survived swimming and sunscreen all week. Looked so real people kept asking where I got it done.</p>\n        <p class=\"review-author\">— Layla H.</p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"review-card\">\n        <div class=\"stars\">★★★★★</div>\n        <p class=\"review-text\">Application was way easier than I expected, on and set in under a minute. Held up through the gym and showers for almost two weeks.</p>\n        <p class=\"review-author\">— Karim S.</p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"review-card\">\n        <div class=\"stars\">★★★★☆</div>\n        <p class=\"review-text\">Great detail on the design and it lasted exactly as long as promised. Only wish it came with a bit more ink for touch ups.</p>\n        <p class=\"review-author\">— Maya D.</p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"review-card\">\n        <div class=\"stars\">★★★★★</div>\n        <p class=\"review-text\">Ordered for a friend's bachelorette and everyone wanted their own. Delivery to Beirut was quick and the tattoos looked professional.</p>\n        <p class=\"review-author\">— Sarah A.</p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"review-card\">\n        <div class=\"stars\">★★★★☆</div>\n        <p class=\"review-text\">Skin felt totally fine the whole time, no irritation at all. Took a little longer than 14 days to fully fade on me but still great value.</p>\n        <p class=\"review-author\">— Tarek N.</p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"review-card\">\n        <div class=\"stars\">★★★★★</div>\n        <p class=\"review-text\">This is my third order. The placement guide made it easy to get it centered and it genuinely fooled my coworkers for a week.</p>\n        <p class=\"review-author\">— Rana K.</p>\n      </div>\n\n      <!-- duplicate set for seamless loop -->\n      <div class=\"review-card\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n        <div class=\"stars\">★★★★★</div>\n        <p class=\"review-text\">Applied it before a beach trip and it survived swimming and sunscreen all week. Looked so real people kept asking where I got it done.</p>\n        <p class=\"review-author\">— Layla H.</p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"review-card\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n        <div class=\"stars\">★★★★★</div>\n        <p class=\"review-text\">Application was way easier than I expected, on and set in under a minute. Held up through the gym and showers for almost two weeks.</p>\n        <p class=\"review-author\">— Karim S.</p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"review-card\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n        <div class=\"stars\">★★★★☆</div>\n        <p class=\"review-text\">Great detail on the design and it lasted exactly as long as promised. Only wish it came with a bit more ink for touch ups.</p>\n        <p class=\"review-author\">— Maya D.</p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"review-card\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n        <div class=\"stars\">★★★★★</div>\n        <p class=\"review-text\">Ordered for a friend's bachelorette and everyone wanted their own. Delivery to Beirut was quick and the tattoos looked professional.</p>\n        <p class=\"review-author\">— Sarah A.</p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"review-card\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n        <div class=\"stars\">★★★★☆</div>\n        <p class=\"review-text\">Skin felt totally fine the whole time, no irritation at all. Took a little longer than 14 days to fully fade on me but still great value.</p>\n        <p class=\"review-author\">— Tarek N.</p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"review-card\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n        <div class=\"stars\">★★★★★</div>\n        <p class=\"review-text\">This is my third order. The placement guide made it easy to get it centered and it genuinely fooled my coworkers for a week.</p>\n        <p class=\"review-author\">— Rana K.</p>\n      </div>\n\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<style>\n  .reviews-section {\n    background: #ffffff;\n    color: #000000;\n    padding: 56px 0;\n    overflow: hidden;\n  }\n\n  .reviews-heading {\n    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", Arial, sans-serif;\n    font-size: 26px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    letter-spacing: -0.01em;\n    color: #000000;\n    margin: 0 0 32px;\n    text-align: center;\n    padding: 0 24px;\n  }\n\n  .reviews-track-wrap {\n    width: 100%;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    mask-image: linear-gradient(to right, transparent 0, #000 48px, #000 calc(100% - 48px), transparent 100%);\n    -webkit-mask-image: linear-gradient(to right, transparent 0, #000 48px, #000 calc(100% - 48px), transparent 100%);\n  }\n\n  .reviews-track {\n    display: flex;\n    gap: 20px;\n    width: max-content;\n    animation: scroll-reviews 38s linear infinite;\n  }\n\n  .reviews-track-wrap:hover .reviews-track {\n    animation-play-state: paused;\n  }\n\n  @keyframes scroll-reviews {\n    from { transform: translateX(0); }\n    to { transform: translateX(-50%); }\n  }\n\n  .review-card {\n    flex: 0 0 auto;\n    width: 280px;\n    background: #ffffff;\n    border: 1px solid #e2e2e2;\n    border-radius: 8px;\n    padding: 22px;\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    gap: 10px;\n  }\n\n  .stars {\n    color: #000000;\n    font-size: 15px;\n    letter-spacing: 2px;\n  }\n\n  .review-text {\n    margin: 0;\n    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", Arial, sans-serif;\n    font-size: 14px;\n    line-height: 1.6;\n    color: #2a2a2a;\n    flex-grow: 1;\n  }\n\n  .review-author {\n    margin: 0;\n    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", Arial, sans-serif;\n    font-size: 13px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    color: #000000;\n  }\n\n  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {\n    .reviews-track {\n      animation: none;\n      overflow-x: auto;\n    }\n  }\n\n  @media (max-width: 480px) {\n    .reviews-heading { font-size: 22px; }\n    .review-card { width: 240px; padding: 18px; }\n  }\n</style>",
